inlet.description:
0 stops playback;
1 starts playback (from beginning of file);
bang reverses current state (i.e. if playing, stops it; if stopped, starts playing);
loop 1/0 turns playback looping on/off.

0 pauses playback;
1 unpauses playback;
bang reverses current state (i.e. if playing, pauses it; if paused, unpauses).
